                            无处
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        




<div style="text-align: right;"><div class="page-rate-widget-box"><span class="rate-points">评分:&nbsp;<span class="number prw54353">+20</span></span><span class="rateup btn btn-default"><a title="我喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, 1)">+</a></span><span class="ratedown btn btn-default"><a title="我不喜欢" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.rate(event, -1)">&#8211;</a></span><span class="cancel btn btn-default"><a title="取消我的投票" href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.modules.PageRateWidgetModule.listeners.cancelVote(event)">x</a></span></div></div>
<div style="border:solid 1px #999999; background:#f2f2c2; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:larger;"><strong>基金会反感知部门在此广播</strong></span></p>
<p>现实存在一畸变处，当前已对抽象事物的形象性产生阻隔，人员需填写此清单以完成该影响规模调查</p>
</div>
</div>
<h5 id="toc0"><span>以下哪个为项目编号？</span></h5>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">A.&nbsp;SCP-CN-1703</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">空腔开始虚设，数个月以来，它的重定位一刻未停，位址再三组合</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>若是对方携带了内部护具，它亦会直接将位在下方的反馈枢纽烧绝</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">B.&nbsp;SCP-3930</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>“无处”像印象派画家的调色盘，鬃毛蜷曲，存在严重透视错误，尽头与云霄媾合，仿佛上下颚交替陈述旧日的胶着，此刻为极寒簇拥。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">C.&nbsp;SCP-CN-xxx</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Cynaik是第一个YRA单元，为在现世存活，一经部署便叛逃至不可见暗面，并且由于二者出自同一中心概念，它可以如领袖机关精准定位自身般定位对方，这是反向自杀。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h5 id="toc1"><span>以下哪个为项目等级？</span></h5>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">A.&nbsp;Keter</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Cynaik常说，倘若一个图像由从各个角度拼凑而成的独立元素组建，就像利用了视线的错觉，有同构异形性，它是反馈。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">B.&nbsp;Confession</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>地球散逸层，实体接触边界临界点，先兆出现于两个朝下折曲的界限中间，闪光在其穿过裂隙时释放，形同氖灯构筑的霓虹。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">C.&nbsp;未分级</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">它恐惧自己的结局如其所说</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>人的思维能力边界也是他实践能力的边界，若令一个人的思维狭隘化，亦会导致此人的实践活动局限在微小范围展开，这种对狭隘的确信将在之后不断加强和重复。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h5 id="toc2"><span>以下哪个为特殊收容措施？</span></h5>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">A.&nbsp;标准人形隔间&nbsp;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>YRA单元一生只会实装一次，被赋予了以世纪为单位的余寿去追杀目标</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">B.&nbsp;SCP-2000</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">它恐惧自己的闪烁于河中隐没</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>桑氏伪齿鸟划过这片灰色的流域，水面如刀鳞，在无数次轮回内映射出了很多东西，一个样态，深洋沉入退行之中，天葬，身体空腔，可能曾具有的更好选择。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">C.&nbsp;编制被取消，项目是否被收容就结果而言没有宏观上的差异</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>或许他曾作为潜在威胁而泯灭在逆行的河中</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h5 id="toc3"><span>以下哪个为描述？</span></h5>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">A.&nbsp;梦之光滑唾沫</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">空腔已抵达远方</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>这是一场没有胜算的战斗，你觉得能在它的终点找到答案吗？</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">B.&nbsp;绝望社恐实验品</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>他们手持深色直伞，风衣里面是董事套装，被一圈光栅箍着，雨从上方倾泻，伞柄是湿的。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">C.&nbsp;残暴反常血块</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>真理埋葬了整个世界</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h5 id="toc4"><span>应做的事是？</span></h5>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">A.&nbsp;葬礼</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>“那个未来从没发生，”Cynaik说，“我在它里面，你注定死亡，你们一定死，这与收容并不冲突。”</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">B.&nbsp;忏悔</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>它是一种虚设，预表并由你破碎的人生直接介入，体现在现实的中心缺失</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">C.&nbsp;重启</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">它将要现身</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>更替之后你会成为谁？你将是无，漆黑，明灭，于时间内掀起褶皱，屏蔽居处——直到什么都不是</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h5 id="toc5"><span>以下哪个命题为真？</span></h5>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">A.&nbsp;今天是周三</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">你并不我</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>更加尖锐地赋形它的，是遭到赋形的自己本身，它以赋形自己的方式赋形自己，在洞开过后，被漆黑取而代之</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">A.&nbsp;蓝色比红色更令人发狂</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">你却很我</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>男人盯着天花板出神，他有一对洁如明镜的淡琥珀色瞳孔，足以看清那长柱，连接两个界面，尘滓蠢动，草坪软簌，像水母摆荡</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">A.&nbsp;人渴望死亡</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">你是否我</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>二月三十日，阴霾居高临下地审视这个世界。像道漆黑的彩虹，颜色乖张，腐败开始凋谢，如见神明，似乎忘却了渡船，群岛寥落，空间依然辉煌</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h5 id="toc6"><span>请欣赏短诗《通天》</span></h5>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">X.&nbsp;欣赏</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">欣赏中</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<blockquote>
<p>我肛门正逐渐通天</p>
<p>坍缩为白矮星</p>
<p>而我的阴茎当前是红巨星</p>
<p>所以我是神</p>
<p>肏系者</p>
<p>我用包皮系带在冠状沟上拉门德尔松E小调协奏曲</p>
<p>是不是神</p>
<p>好像是神</p>
<p>我甚至可以肏图</p>
<p>我之肏无视尺度</p>
<p>尺度越大我肏得越狠</p>
<p>反之精密度更高<br />
我肏开了天球</p>
<p>天球的阴道里全是费米子白带</p>
<p>然后我开始肏月背</p>
<p>月背现大坑</p>
<p>那个坑叫<em>The Abyss</em></p>
<p>每日九时准确潮喷</p>
<p>单数日喷月经</p>
<p>双数日喷巴氏腺液</p>
<p>安息日大吸</p>
<p>回收伏笔</p>
<p>我称其为人的噩梦</p>
</blockquote>
<p>你们都知道结局如何</p>
